OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with rain and
OL,6,Fdrizzle over the west at first
OL,7,Fspreading to all parts through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Rain will be heavy at times
OL,9,Fin the morning but turning lighter and
OL,10,Fpatchier later. Breezy near western
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain. Staying mostly
OL,15,Fcloudy overnight with rain turning
OL,16,Fmore showery and a few clearer spells
OL,17,Fdeveloping between showers in the
OL,18,Fwest. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
