OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with a few
OL,6,Fbright spells and frequent showers
OL,7,Ffeeding in from the west. Showers
OL,8,Fheavy at times and forming longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain later. Windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy on Saturday with heavy
OL,13,Fshowers clearing later in the day. Dry
OL,14,Fon Sunday and Monday with some long
OL,15,Fspells of sunshine. Becoming warmer in
OL,16,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
